site.enquiryText: Interested in this property? Our team of dedicated industry experts is here to help you. Fill out the form below or call 020 7736 7133 to get in touch.

entries.title: 2 Bedroom Flat, 163 New Kings Road
entries.propertyDescription:
A spacious, furnished, one bedroom apartment situated on the first floor of a handsome refurbished Edwardian building. Situated on the Peterborough Estate on New Kings Road with views over Eel Brook common from the reception room.

The property comprises of an entrance hall, reception with open plan kitchen including built in fridge freezer, electric hob & gas oven, dishwasher and washer dryer, large double bedroom with an ensuite shower room, bathroom with power shower over bath and a good size study/ second bedroom.

Less than a 5 minute walk to either Fulham Broadway or Parsons Green tube station.

entries.title: 2 Bedroom Flat, Wandsworth Bridge Road
entries.propertyDescription:
A spacious and fully furnished, two bed, two bath, split level apartment on Wandsworth Bridge Road, SW6.

The property consists of a bright open plan living room and kitchen. The kitchen is fully fitted with an integrated dishwasher and washer dryer, gas hob and electric oven. The living space is bright and airy with wooden floors and there is use of a communal satellite capable of HD and multi room. All windows are double glazed.

The apartment is ideal for professional sharers with 2 double bedrooms, the master bedroom is well proportioned with and has ample wardrobe and under-bed storage with an en-suite shower room. The second bedroom also has ample wardrobe and under-bed storage. Large family bathroom with power shower over the bath and storage.

The flat is approximately 10 minutes from Fulham Broadway tube and 15 minutes to Parsons Green.

entries.title: 1 Bedroom Flat, 65 New Kings Road, SW6
2 Bedroom Maisonette, Hugon Road, SW6
entries.propertyDescription:
A spacious, two bedroom, furnished, split level flat in a terraced Victorian house. Large kitchen/breakfast room, living room, bathroom with power shower, separate WC and two double bedrooms with fitted wardrobes.

Nearest tube Fulham Broadway or Wandsworth Town British Rail. Buses 295,28 & C3.

Nearest train station Imperial Wharf or Wandsworth Town BR.

entries.title: 2 Bedroom Flat, Elmar Court, SW6
entries.propertyDescription: This spacious, fully furnished, two-bedroom flat is located on Fulham Road very close to local amenities, including Sainsbury's local across the road. The flat comprises a large living and dining space with plenty of natural light, separate modern fully integrated kitchen, bathroom, large master bedroom with ample storage and a second double bedroom with built-in storage. It further benefits from plenty of hallway storage and access to a well-maintained communal garden.

entries.title: 2 Bedroom Flat, Stephendale Road, SW6
entries.propertyDescription:
A lovely, two bed, ground floor furnished flat in an end of terrace Victorian house on Stephendale Road in Fulham, SW6.

The flat comprises of a large kitchen/ reception room with all appliances, 2 double bedrooms and bathroom with a large shower. There is also a large enclosed courtyard at the front of the property.

Nearest tube Fulham Broadway or Parsons Green - Wandsworth Town British Rail. Buses 28 and 295.

entries.title: 2 Bedroom Flat, Wandsworth Bridge Road, SW6
entries.propertyDescription: A large, split level, two bedroom flat with balcony. The flat features a large living room and separate eat in kitchen. Both bedrooms are spacious with good storage.

entries.title: 2 Bedroom Flat, Hugon Road, SW6
entries.propertyDescription: Recently refurbished, spacious, two bedroom ground floor flat with large garden. The flat comprises of a large living/ dining space which opens onto a secluded, private garden via bi-fold doors. There are two double bedrooms, a family bathroom and separate shower room.

entries.title: 1 Bedroom Flat, Magdalen Road
entries.propertyDescription:
A spacious newly refurbished one bedroom flat with private entrance and large garden, located on Magdalen Road, moments from Earlsfield mainline station. The flat comprises of a bright living room to the front of the property and a newly fitted integrated kitchen with space for a dining table. The bedroom and bathroom are to the rear of the property.

The flat further benefits from a large private garden. Please note the property is unfurnished and the photos have been virtually staged.
